---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Synth — Deployment Intelligence, Embedded" description="Synth is an intelligent deployment system. You say what and where — Synth reasons about the how, produces a plan, and explains every decision. Open source, self-hosted.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-ds-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-ds-partition/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-24 pb-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left: tagline + CTAs -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up text-center lg:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem] font-display font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
            You say <span class="text-ds-accent">what</span> and <span class="text-ds-accent">where</span>.<br />
            Synth figures out the <span class="text-ds-accent">how</span>.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-ds-text-secondary max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            An intelligent deployment system that reasons about your artifacts,
            produces a plan, and explains every decision before it touches a thing.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 mb-8">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/synth-deploy/synth-deploy"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="rounded-md bg-ds-accent px-6 py-3 text-ds-bg font-semibold hover:bg-ds-accent/90 transition-colors"
            >
              Get Started
            </a>
            <a
              href="/docs"
              class="rounded-md border border-ds-border px-6 py-3 text-ds-text hover:border-ds-accent-border hover:bg-ds-surface transition-colors"
            >
              Read the Docs
            </a>
            <a href="/roadmap" class="rounded-md border border-ds-border px-6 py-3 text-ds-text-secondary hover:border-ds-accent-border hover:bg-ds-surface transition-colors">
              Roadmap
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-muted">Source-available&ensp;·&ensp;Self-hosted&ensp;·&ensp;MCP-native</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: animated demo -->
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-2">
          <div id="hero-demo" class="glass-card accent-glow overflow-hidden text-left relative" style="min-height: 420px;">
            <!-- Fake window chrome -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2.5 border-b border-ds-border bg-ds-bg/40">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ds-failed/40"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ds-warning/40"></span>
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded/40"></span>
              <span class="ml-3 text-[10px] font-mono text-ds-text-muted">Synth</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 1: Artifact intake — drag-in -->
            <div id="stage-intake" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted mb-4">Artifact Intake</p>
              <div id="drop-zone" class="rounded-lg border-2 border-dashed border-ds-border flex items-center justify-center" style="height: 120px;">
                <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-muted">Drop an artifact to begin</p>
              </div>
              <div id="artifact-card" class="artifact-dragging absolute rounded-lg border border-ds-accent-border bg-ds-surface px-4 py-3" style="right: -200px; top: 80px;">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-ds-accent/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-ds-accent text-xs font-bold">C</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ds-text">payments-api</p>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">v2.4.1 · container</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 2: Analysis -->
            <div id="stage-analysis" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5 hidden">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted mb-4">Analyzing Artifact</p>
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-ds-accent-border bg-ds-accent/5 px-4 py-3 mb-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-ds-accent/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-ds-accent text-xs font-bold">C</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ds-text">payments-api</p>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">v2.4.1 · container</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div id="analysis-lines" class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs">
                <p class="analysis-line text-ds-text-muted opacity-0"><span class="text-ds-dt-scan">■</span> Detected: Docker container image</p>
                <p class="analysis-line text-ds-text-muted opacity-0"><span class="text-ds-dt-config">■</span> Base: node:20-alpine · 3 layers</p>
                <p class="analysis-line text-ds-text-muted opacity-0"><span class="text-ds-dt-plan">■</span> Ports: 3000/tcp · Health: /health</p>
                <p class="analysis-line text-ds-text-muted opacity-0"><span class="text-ds-succeeded">■</span> Checksum verified · No CVEs found</p>
              </div>
              <div id="analysis-bar" class="mt-4 h-1 rounded-full bg-ds-border overflow-hidden">
                <div class="analysis-progress h-full rounded-full bg-ds-accent" style="width: 0%"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 3: Select envoy/target -->
            <div id="stage-select" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5 hidden">
              <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted mb-4">Select Target</p>
              <div class="rounded-lg border border-ds-accent-border bg-ds-accent/5 px-4 py-2.5 mb-4">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ds-text">payments-api <span class="text-ds-text-muted font-normal">v2.4.1</span></p>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div id="envoy-row-1" class="envoy-row flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-ds-border px-4 py-3 transition-all duration-300 cursor-default">
                  <div class="entity-badge border-ds-envoy/30 bg-ds-envoy/10 text-ds-envoy text-[10px] py-0.5">Envoy</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm text-ds-text">prod-us-east</p>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-ds-text-muted">3 containers · healthy</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded"></span>
                </div>
                <div id="envoy-row-2" class="envoy-row flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-ds-border px-4 py-3 opacity-50 cursor-default">
                  <div class="entity-badge border-ds-envoy/30 bg-ds-envoy/10 text-ds-envoy text-[10px] py-0.5">Envoy</div>
                  <div class="flex-1">
                    <p class="text-sm text-ds-text">staging-eu-west</p>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-ds-text-muted">1 container · healthy</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded"></span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 4: Plan generation -->
            <div id="stage-plan" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5 hidden">
              <div class="mb-3">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted mb-1">Deployment Plan</p>
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-ds-text leading-tight">payments-api <span class="text-sm font-normal text-ds-text-muted">&rarr; prod-us-east</span></p>
              </div>
              <!-- Assessment -->
              <div id="plan-assessment" class="rounded-lg border border-ds-border bg-ds-bg/60 px-4 py-3 mb-4 opacity-0">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-1">
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted">Synth Assessment</span>
                  <span class="flex-1 h-0.5 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded/60"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-ds-succeeded">High</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary leading-snug">Proceed — target is stable, no conflicts</p>
              </div>
              <!-- Steps -->
              <div class="space-y-0">
                <div class="plan-step flex items-start gap-3 py-2 border-b border-ds-border/50 opacity-0">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded/15 text-ds-succeeded text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">1</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text leading-snug flex-1">Pull image &amp; verify checksum</p>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-ds-succeeded/70 font-medium">low</span>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-step flex items-start gap-3 py-2 border-b border-ds-border/50 opacity-0">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded/15 text-ds-succeeded text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">2</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text leading-snug flex-1">Stop existing container</p>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-ds-succeeded/70 font-medium">low</span>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-step flex items-start gap-3 py-2 border-b border-ds-border/50 opacity-0">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-failed/15 text-ds-failed text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">3</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text leading-snug flex-1">Remove container &amp; free port</p>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-ds-failed/70 font-medium">high</span>
                </div>
                <div class="plan-step flex items-start gap-3 py-2 opacity-0">
                  <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-succeeded/15 text-ds-succeeded text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">4</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text leading-snug flex-1">Run new container with env</p>
                  <span class="text-[10px] text-ds-succeeded/70 font-medium">low</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Greenlight button -->
              <div id="plan-actions" class="mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-ds-border/50 opacity-0">
                <button id="greenlight-btn" class="w-full rounded-md bg-ds-succeeded/15 border border-ds-succeeded/25 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ds-succeeded cursor-default">Greenlight</button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 5: Execution -->
            <div id="stage-exec" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5 hidden">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ds-text-muted">Executing</p>
                <span class="exec-spinner w-3 h-3 rounded-full border-2 border-ds-accent border-t-transparent"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-0">
                <div class="exec-step flex items-center gap-3 py-2.5 border-b border-ds-border/50">
                  <span class="exec-icon flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-border text-ds-text-muted text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary flex-1">Pull image &amp; verify checksum</p>
                  <span class="exec-status text-[10px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">waiting</span>
                </div>
                <div class="exec-step flex items-center gap-3 py-2.5 border-b border-ds-border/50">
                  <span class="exec-icon flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-border text-ds-text-muted text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary flex-1">Stop existing container</p>
                  <span class="exec-status text-[10px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">waiting</span>
                </div>
                <div class="exec-step flex items-center gap-3 py-2.5 border-b border-ds-border/50">
                  <span class="exec-icon flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-border text-ds-text-muted text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary flex-1">Remove container &amp; free port</p>
                  <span class="exec-status text-[10px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">waiting</span>
                </div>
                <div class="exec-step flex items-center gap-3 py-2.5">
                  <span class="exec-icon flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-ds-border text-ds-text-muted text-[10px] font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary flex-1">Run new container with env</p>
                  <span class="exec-status text-[10px] text-ds-text-muted font-mono">waiting</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 6: Debrief -->
            <div id="stage-debrief" class="demo-stage px-5 pt-5 pb-5 hidden">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                <div class="entity-badge border-ds-debrief/30 bg-ds-debrief/10 text-ds-debrief text-[10px] py-0.5">Debrief</div>
                <span class="text-xs text-ds-text-muted ml-auto">payments-api v2.4.1 &rarr; prod-us-east</span>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-0">
                <div class="debrief-entry flex gap-2.5 pb-3 relative opacity-0">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-plan mt-1"></span>
                    <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-ds-dt-plan uppercase tracking-wide">Pipeline Plan</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Planned 4-step pipeline for container deployment</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="debrief-entry flex gap-2.5 pb-3 relative opacity-0">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-config mt-1"></span>
                    <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-ds-dt-config uppercase tracking-wide">Configuration</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Resolved 3 variables — no conflicts detected</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="debrief-entry flex gap-2.5 pb-3 relative opacity-0">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-execution mt-1"></span>
                    <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-ds-dt-execution uppercase tracking-wide">Execution</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">All 4 steps completed in 12.3s</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="debrief-entry flex gap-2.5 pb-3 relative opacity-0">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-verification mt-1"></span>
                    <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-ds-dt-verification uppercase tracking-wide">Verification</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Health check passed — HTTP 200 on /health in 42ms</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="debrief-entry flex gap-2.5 relative opacity-0">
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-completion mt-1"></span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-ds-dt-completion uppercase tracking-wide">Completed</p>
                    <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Deployment succeeded — all checks passed</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Pause on hover indicator -->
            <div id="demo-paused" class="absolute inset-0 bg-ds-bg/60 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200">
              <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-muted">Paused — move cursor to resume</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: Simple Setup -->
  <section id="features" class="py-28 border-t border-ds-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="section-heading">Simple to Set Up</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">Two components. One command.</h2>
        <p class="text-ds-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Synth runs as two lightweight services — the Synth server and Envoy — that communicate
          over HTTP. No complex infrastructure. No vendor lock-in. Self-hosted by design.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Synth server card -->
        <div class="glass-card p-8 scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="entity-badge border-ds-server/30 bg-ds-server/10 text-ds-server">
              Synth
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">The brain</h3>
          <p class="text-ds-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Central server that manages operations, partitions, and environments.
            Runs the intelligent agent, exposes the REST API, and hosts the MCP server.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 font-mono text-xs text-ds-text-muted bg-ds-bg/50 rounded-md px-4 py-3">
            docker run synth-deploy/server
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Envoy card -->
        <div class="glass-card p-8 scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="entity-badge border-ds-envoy/30 bg-ds-envoy/10 text-ds-envoy">
              Envoy
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">The hands</h3>
          <p class="text-ds-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Lightweight agents deployed on target machines. Execute deployment steps,
            run health checks, and report results back to Synth.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 font-mono text-xs text-ds-text-muted bg-ds-bg/50 rounded-md px-4 py-3">
            docker run synth-deploy/envoy
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Intelligent Decisions -->
  <section class="py-28 border-t border-ds-border relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-ds-dt-plan/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-ds-debrief/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="section-heading">Intelligent Decisions</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">Every action explained. Every decision logged.</h2>
        <p class="text-ds-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The agent resolves variables, plans pipelines, handles conflicts, and diagnoses
          failures — then explains all of it in plain language. When something goes wrong
          at 2am, the Debrief tells you exactly what happened.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Decision type showcase -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="glass-card p-6 scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-plan"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ds-dt-plan">Pipeline Plan</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Agent analyzed web-app v2.4.1 and planned a 3-step pipeline:
            install, migrate, verify. Skipped cache-warmup — no Redis configured.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6 scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-conflict"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ds-dt-conflict">Variable Conflict</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            APP_ENV defined in both partition (production) and environment (staging).
            Resolved using environment-wins policy. Logged both values for audit.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card p-6 scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-diagnostic"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-ds-dt-diagnostic">Diagnostic</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Health check failed on attempt 1/3 (ECONNREFUSED on port 9410).
            Root cause: migration step increased startup time. Retried after 5s — passed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Debrief timeline mockup -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto scroll-reveal scroll-reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="glass-card accent-glow overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3 border-b border-ds-border">
            <div class="entity-badge border-ds-debrief/30 bg-ds-debrief/10 text-ds-debrief text-[10px] py-0.5">
              Debrief
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs text-ds-text-muted ml-auto">web-app v2.4.1 &rarr; acme-corp / production</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 space-y-0">
            <!-- Timeline entries -->
            <div class="flex gap-3 pb-4 relative">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-plan mt-1"></span>
                <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-ds-dt-plan uppercase tracking-wide">Pipeline Plan</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Planned 3-step pipeline for web-app v2.4.1</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-muted mt-1">Steps: install-deps &rarr; run-migrations &rarr; health-check</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-3 pb-4 relative">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-config mt-1"></span>
                <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-ds-border mt-1"></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-ds-dt-config uppercase tracking-wide">Configuration</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-ds-text-secondary mt-0.5">Resolved 4 variables across partition and environment</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-ds-text-muted mt-1">1 conflict: APP_ENV — environment value wins (staging)</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-3 pb-4 relative">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="dt-dot bg-ds-dt-execution mt-1"></span>
